Robots

* bully
	scan in 2 deg intervals, if find a robot launch missile, shield on and move half way to the robot (minimum 25 away)
* evade
	scan in 2 deg intervals, if find a robot launch missile
* evade_plus
	as evade but launch and move a short distance then work out where robot was ready to launch again
* dumb
	just sit there
* random
	move randomly, scan once, move again
* corner
	pick a random corner, go to it, then scan and launch missiles, never move from that corner
